title: GO SMS PRO X Factor Theme
creator: Jason Kench

extendedInfo.description: Available Now! - X Factor Theme for GO SMS Pro - Offers FREE updates.Bright, colourful, clean graphical theme which will give you that X Factor feel. High quality graphics and design will bring your messaging experience back to life.I hope you enjoy!*****************************************QUICK AND EASY THEME INSTALLATION - *****************************************1. To apply the theme firstly download GO SMS Pro for free. (Search for "GO SMS PRO" in the Play Store. Download and install.)2. Now download this theme.3. Once downloaded open "Go SMS Pro" app and then press the "Menu Button" (The bottom left button on the phone).4. Press "Theme"5. Then at the top of the screen there will be two buttons: "Featured" and "Installed". Press "Installed".6. Now scroll through the list of installed themes until you see this one.7. Press on the theme picture and press "apply".8. Now press the "Back" button bottom right and go back to the main messaging window and you will see the theme has been changed.It is as simple as that. If you have any problems please use the email address below to message me and I will try my best to respond quickly.*****************************************RATE THE THEME*****************************************Please rate the theme :)If there is a problem please dont leave a bad rating, email me first as I will be happy to help.*****************************************PROBLEMS*****************************************If there is a problem with the theme please contact me via email with as plenty of detail and I will do my best to help you with the problem.*****************************************FEEDBACK & SUGGESTIONS*****************************************If you would like to let me know any feedback, comments, suggestions, problems or design ideas then please feel free: jkench@jasonkench.co.ukIs there a theme you would like to see produced? If so please email me with the ideas and I will see if there is a demand for that theme.*****************************************CONTACT*****************************************Jason Kench - jkench@jasonkench.co.ukDesigned and developed by Jason Kench.
